title: Lexi Thompson wins LPGA Tour event in South Korea
text: Lexi Thompson wins LPGA Tour event in South Korea Sunday, 18 October 2015 (8 minutes ago) INCHEON, South Korea (AP) " Lexi Thompson broke out of a crowded pack Sunday to win the LPGA KEB Hana Bank Championship for her second victory of the year and sixth overall.The 20-year-old American closed with a 3-under 69 to beat...
